---
// src/components/Footer.astro
---

<footer class="footer">
  <p class="footer-text">
    Made with <span>❤️</span> and tears | 每一个死去的项目都是通往成功的垫脚石<br/>
    © 2024 Cyber Code Graveyard - 纪念所有失败的尝试
  </p>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-bg-base) 40%, transparent);
    margin-top: 60px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .footer-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
  }

  .footer-text span {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    display: inline-block;
    animation: pulseHeart 1s infinite alternate;
  }

  @keyframes pulseHeart {
    0% { transform: scale(1); }
    100% { transform: scale(1.2); }
  }
</style>
